CompanyName.value: Eaton Vance Enhance Equity Income Fund

CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Eaton Vance Enhanced Equity Income Fund offers mutual funds that invest across a wide array of equity, income and alternative strategies. The Fund pursues its investment objectives by investing primarily in a portfolio of mid- and large-capitalization common stocks. Under normal market conditions, the Fund seeks to generate current earnings from option premiums by selling covered call options on a substantial portion of its portfolio securities.
